      <title>随着信贷增长，阿波罗私人财富管理业务创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/apollo-raises-record-from-private-wealth-as-credit-lures-clients</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 挖掘富裕客户潜力的计划正在取得成效，其财富业务去年吸金创下纪录，该领域资产增长了 50%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/apollo-raises-record-from-private-wealth-as-credit-lures-clients</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
